Name: Bob's Cat Challenge
About the game: Oh no! The cats have gotten loose - and it's up to our hero, Bob the Yeti, to collect them all! While trying to rescue all the lost felines, Bob must face upcoming dangers such as falling platforms, rolling snowballs and slippy ice bricks - not to mention some of the unleashed cats themselves! Is Bob up to the challenge? Inspired by the classic platformers from the past decades, Bob's Cat Challenge offers an exciting 3D adventure for players of all ages!
